Info - How to setup Chart <pre><code>import pandas as pd
from ipyvizzu import Chart, Data, Config, Style

df = pd.read_csv(
    "https://ipyvizzu.vizzuhq.com/0.17/assets/data/chart_types_eu_data_6.csv",
    dtype={"Year": str, "Timeseries": str},
)
data = Data()
data.add_df(df)

chart = Chart()
chart.animate(data)</code></pre> <ul> <li>remove the Dimension from Y-axis</li> <li>set the Align parameter from 'stretch' to 'min'</li> <li>switch the Geometry from Area to Line</li> </ul> <pre><code>chart.animate(
    Config(
        {
            "channels": {
                "x": "Year",
                "y": ["Value 2 (+)", "Country"],
                "color": "Country",
            },
            "geometry": "area",
            "align": "stretch",
        }
    )
)

chart.animate(
    Config(
        {
            "channels": {"y": "Value 2 (+)"},
            "geometry": "line",
            "align": "min",
        }
    )
)

chart.feature("tooltip", True)</code></pre>

