Info - How to setup Chart <pre><code>import pandas as pd
from ipyvizzu import Chart, Data, Config, Style

df = pd.read_csv(
    "https://ipyvizzu.vizzuhq.com/0.17/assets/data/chart_types_eu_data_4.csv",
    dtype={"Year": str, "Timeseries": str},
)
data = Data()
data.add_df(df)

chart = Chart()
chart.animate(data)</code></pre> <ul> <li>move the 2nd Dimension from X-axis to the Y-axis</li> <li>add the Measure to the Label channel too</li> </ul> <pre><code>chart.animate(
    Config(
        {
            "channels": {
                "x": ["Year", "Country"],
                "y": "Value 2 (+)",
                "color": "Country",
            },
            "geometry": "rectangle",
        }
    )
)

chart.animate(
    Config(
        {
            "channels": {
                "x": "Year",
                "y": ["Country", "Value 2 (+)"],
                "label": "Value 2 (+)",
            },
            "split": True,
        }
    ),
    Style(
        {
            "plot": {
                "marker": {
                    "label": {"position": "top", "fontSize": "0.6em"}
                }
            }
        }
    ),
)

chart.feature("tooltip", True)</code></pre>

