chart.animate(data)</code></pre> <p>This Vizzu animation consist of 2 steps (animates):</p> <p>1st:</p> <ul> <li>move the Dimension from X-axis to the Y-axis</li> <li>add a new Dimension to the X-axis</li> <li>remove the Measure from the label channel</li> </ul> <p>2nd:</p> <ul> <li>move the Measure from X to Y-axis</li> </ul> <pre><code>chart.animate(
